Licensing for the config/ directory
====================================

This directory contains two files with different licenses:

1. config.yml — Apache License 2.0

   Runtime application configuration (database paths, Ollama settings,
   defense level defaults, RAG parameters). This is infrastructure
   configuration and is licensed under the same Apache License 2.0 as the
   rest of the platform code.

   See the root LICENSE file for the full Apache 2.0 text.

2. labs.yml — Creative Commons BY-NC-SA 4.0

   Attack lab definitions, scenario descriptions, and educational content.
   This is training material and is licensed under the Creative Commons
   Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.

   You may use labs.yml for personal learning, academic research, and
   non-commercial purposes. Commercial use — including paid courses,
   workshops, or certification programs — requires permission from the
   maintainers.

   Full license text:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/legalcode

For commercial licensing inquiries, see TRAINING_LICENSE.md in the
project root or contact the maintainers via:
https://github.com/AISecurityConsortium/AIGoat
